## Get Direct Down Link Of Fm-Mods From fouadmods.net

- Owner : [Vihanga-YT](https://github.com/vihangayt0)

***

## Example
```js
const { mods } = require('fouadwa-scraper')

let getmod = await mods()
console.log(getmod)
```
***
